'''''The Marvel Comics Illustrated Version of Return of the Jedi''''' collects issues 1-4 in the [[Star Wars (1977)|Marvel ''Star Wars'']] comics ''Return of the Jedi'' series. It is a complete comic book adaption of [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']], and is a 4 1/8 by 7 inch paperback novel sized comic.

